data.description: Don't miss this Fully Updated, Meticulously Cared For Home in a Great Location. Spacious Updated Kitchen with Granite Countertops and Backsplash. New Kitchen Sink and Disposal. Updated Bathrooms with Granite Countertops and Soaker Master Tub. Walk in Closet in Master Bedroom. All Updated Vinyl Flooring, Carpet Upstairs, Paint, Baseboards, Water Heater, Water Softener, Ceiling Fans, Garage Door Opener, Thermostat and Window Coverings. This home is immaculate!  The HOA will allow you to fence in the yard if you'd like. No Restrictions on Renting the Property. No Restrictons on Pets.
